{
  "stem": "10587.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, Joshua, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, they were talking about hiding, starting to hide, so that-- because they were taking transports every day from [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shodula ?] to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I was-- I, I, I knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I even knew where they took my mother with this, you know, because my father immediately said that's where they took her, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not aware of, of any kind of construction going on in, in what used to be a, a--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barracks for a-- for the Polish army, yes, camp, Polish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we-- that's all they talked about, you know, that they are sending the people to Auschwitz, to-- and the old people are being gassed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and it was a-- like an open secret, yeah, in [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shodula, ?] you know, that-- and they, and some people are sent to, to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some people are sent to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For hiding, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what they did is, is they, they closed off the, the, the normal entries to the basement.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they, they cut a hole in, in, in the floor in one of the apartments, and, and put a ladder down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the-- and on top of the, the opening, go through to the-- opening to the basement, they nailed a, a table and a carpet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every time you open it up, you move the table away to go down there, and then-- and a chair.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then you moved it back so it looked like that there is nothing below.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when it got to the point that we-- that the time came to hide, because we were concerned, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- as I told you before, the-- depends on the-- they were always scattering people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So with my father's background, they, they-- you know, depends who you talk to, and, and what kind of a person.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would say, [GERMAN SPEECH]?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or they would say, [GERMAN SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You-- excuse my expression-- shitty Jew and, and give him a few [INAUDIBLE] on, on his face.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so he, he realized that the end is, is near to, you know, where they would liquidate [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Shodula. ?] And that was a big concern.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We went down this place in the basement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a whole apparatus, as I said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They cut a hole which fit right back in, in, in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on top of the hole, they put a-- like a rug, which they nailed to it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they nailed a table to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So when they moved it, there was, there is no way to realize that there's a opening below.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was a totally, total fiasco.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they took-- first of all, there was no sanitary facilities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no bathrooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took down some water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- the smell was horrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no air coming in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they were not smart enough to realize to put in a vent somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And maybe they were, however, then they probably were afraid that the Germans would listen to it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they, they, so we went down there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- we were down there maybe a day or two, maybe three days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I told my father, I said, I am not-- I don't want to be here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, this-- when they find that we are here, hiding, they will throw in one or two grenades and kill everyone there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and I don't want to die this way, I told him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were-- and so we-- one evening at-- when it got-- when became dark, we walked from [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Shodula ?]-- my father, myself, and my younger brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he must have-- my father must have gotten some maps to, to realize which way to, to go to another camp, another ghetto, which was from Bielsko, not far from Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked-- excuse me-- we walked all night and through the fields, through the cornfields, and through-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] off the beaten path.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And off, off-- so, so there's no roads.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no one could-- and we came there, dead tired, to this place outside of Bielsko thatt was also a, a ghetto, and where my aunt and uncle and, and, and also the youngest brother, and, and, and, and two brothers.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was-- one's name is Jack Rosenbaum, who is still alive, his brother, Shemek, who was about the same age as my brother and, and my aunt and uncle.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they dug a hole in, in-- outside, in a, in a storage bin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and they put a mattress down in the hole.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
